title: Bob Mintzer and Randy Brecker at JEN 2014
description:
http://randybrecker.com/
https://www.facebook.com/RandyBrecker
https://twitter.com/RandyBrecker
Marina Terteryan interviews Bob Mintzer and Randy Brecker at the JEN 2014 Conference in Dallas. For more about the Jazz Education Network, please visit http://jazzednet.org
Purchase the new Brecker Brothers Band Reunion (includes Live Concert DVD)  http://randybrecker.com/recordings/the-brecker-brothers-band-reunion/

Jazz trumpeter and composer Randy Brecker has helped shape the sound of jazz, R&B and rock for more than four decades. His trumpet and flugelhorn performances have graced hundreds of albums by a wide range of artists from James Taylor, Bruce Springsteen and Parliament/Funkadelic to Frank Sinatra, Steely Dan, Jaco Pastorius and Frank Zappa.
